title: #92Noon! Grimm/Gorg/Leber/Motzko/Mick/Zimm/Bruno
description: Full show! A-Topics, Gophers Vox Mike Grimm and FSN's Kevin Gorg make up the first hour...Ben Leber in studio and then Gopher Hockey coach Bob Motzko make up the middle portion...Pat Micheletti in studio, Mike Zimmer's weekly chat with PA and Philly radio icon Tony Bruno cap off a busy Thursday!
